00:26:49,975 --> 00:26:53,172
J‘ No more laughing

252
00:26:53,244 --> 00:26:55,678
J‘ In the sun

253
00:26:57,549 --> 00:27:02,851
J‘ River of moonshine

254
00:27:02,921 --> 00:27:06,322
J‘ I hear your voice

255
00:27:06,391 --> 00:27:09,019
J‘ And it's calling

256
00:27:09,094 --> 00:27:11,329
J‘ But I'm still alone

257
00:27:11,329 --> 00:27:14,890
J‘ But I'm still alone

